QueryText: DECLARE $param1 AS Text; DECLARE $param2 AS Uint64; SELECT t1.id, t1.name, t1.value FROM table_alpha t1 WHERE t1.id=$param1 ORDER BY t1.created_at DESC LIMIT $param2
SELECT t2.id, t2.status, t2.amount FROM table_beta t2 WHERE t2.status = 'active' AND t2.created_at > '2025-01-01'
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM table_gamma GROUP BY category HAVING COUNT(*) > 5
